{
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<section class=\"webinar-detail\">\n<div class=\"webinar-hero-banner hero__container hero__container--text-dark hero__container--no-overlay hero__container--color\">\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<h1 class=\"webinar-title\">\n<span>Beyond the Four Walls: Hidden Homeowners Exposures and the Power of Endorsements</span>\n</h1>\n<span data-item-id=\"82139\" data-price=\"79.00\" data-product=\"Beyond the Four Walls: Hidden Homeowners Exposures and the Power of Endorsements\" data-react-component-id=\"add-to-cart\">\n<button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--disabled\">Add to Cart -\t\t\t\t\t\t&amp;dollar;79.00</button>\n</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width container__flex u-padding-top\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark badge--icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-icon-calendar-dims\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#calendar\"></use>\n</svg>\n<div><time datetime=\"2026-05-19T17:00:00Z\">May. 19 2026 01:00 PM EDT</time>\n</div>\n</span>\n<div class=\"webinar-block u-margin-bottom\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"webinar-description u-padding-bottom\">\n<p>Homeowners coverage is often treated like a quick add-on policy, yet evolving property uses, rising reconstruction costs, and shifting underwriting rules have made it far more complex. Break down dwelling valuation, roof limitations, matching issues, labor depreciation disputes, and contents settlement realities. Examine hidden exposures involving other structures, home-based businesses, and short-term rentals. Through practical examples and endorsement strategies, you will gain tools to identify gaps, manage expectations, and recommend coverage that truly reflects how clients live and work today. </p><ul><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $79.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span><ul><li><em>*CEU Unlimited subscriber webinar discount will be reflected in the checkout process. <span><strong>No discount code or pre-paid agreement number required!</strong></span></em></li></ul></li><li><span>NO State Reporting Fees</span></li><li><span>NO Hidden Fees</span></li></ul>\n</div>\n<span data-item-id=\"82139\" data-price=\"79.00\" data-product=\"Beyond the Four Walls: Hidden Homeowners Exposures and the Power of Endorsements\" data-react-component-id=\"add-to-cart\">\n<button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--disabled\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAdd to Cart - &amp;dollar;79.00\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</button>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"webinar-sponsor\">\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><div data-api-id=\"82139\" data-course-code=\"\" data-react-component-id=\"webinar-ce-information\"></div>\n</div>\n<div><section class=\"star-bar__container u-margin-top container--max-width\">\n<div class=\"alert-message u-padding-hug-left u-bg-accent-lavender u-font-family-primary u-margin-bottom\">\n<span class=\"u-margin-right u-bg-alert-blue\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-color-white\" height=\"24\" role=\"presentation\" width=\"24\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#star\"></use>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"u-padding-right\">Enjoy Every Webinar Free with CEU Unlimited. Scroll Below to Get Your Savings Now.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div> <div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--webinar-detail paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div class=\"views-element-container\">\n<section class=\"js-view-dom-id-a75c81ba66218b2cfe0c36398ed730f1b924767a3a7593f838039e1caef1717b u-padding-md-bottom\">\n<div class=\"filter-exposed-form u-margin-lg-bottom\">\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"views-row\">\n<section class=\"u-padding-lg-bottom\" id=\"add_to_cart\">\n<div class=\"u-padding-md-top u-padding-lg-bottom u-bg-gradient-blue course-details__header\">\n<div class=\"u-padding-md-bottom container container--max-width\">\n<h2 class=\"u-margin-hug u-text-center u-color-white\">Webinar Details</h2>\n<hr class=\"u-margin-top u-margin-bottom hr--centered hr--md hr--white\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<div class=\"container__grid container__grid--centered container__grid--max-md\">\n<article class=\"card__container\">\n<div class=\"card__content\">\n<div class=\"card__header-container\">\n<h4 class=\"u-margin-hug card__title\">Beyond the Four Walls: Hidden Homeowners Exposures and the Power of Endorsements</h4>\n</div>\n<p>Homeowners insurance may look simple, but today’s risks tell a different story. Reveal hidden coverage gaps, valuation pitfalls, and modern property uses that can derail a claim. From roofs and reconstruction costs to endorsements and short-term rentals, learn how to align coverage with real-life exposures. </p>\n<dl class=\"detail-list__container detail-list__container--3-col\">\n<div class=\"detail-list__item\">\n<dt class=\"detail-list__title\">Date and Time</dt>\n<dd class=\"detail-list__desc\">\n<time datetime=\"2026-05-19T13:00:00Z\">May. 19 2026 01:00 PM EDT</time>\n</dd>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"detail-list__item\">\n<dt class=\"detail-list__title\">Webinar Duration</dt>\n<dd class=\"detail-list__desc\">180 minutes</dd>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"detail-list__item\">\n<dt class=\"detail-list__title\">CE Requirements</dt>\n<dd class=\"detail-list__desc\">\n<a href=\"/ceu/state-requirements\" target=\"_blank\">Verify your state and license CE requirements</a>\n</dd>\n</div>\n</dl>\n\n<dl class=\"detail-list__container\">\n<div class=\"detail-list__item\">\n<dt class=\"detail-list__title\">Topics</dt>\n<dd class=\"detail-list__desc\">\n<ul class=\"u-margin-hug\">\n<li>Clarify the critical differences between market value, replacement cost, and actual cash value</li>\n<li>Identify roof limitations, matching concerns, and depreciation challenges that impact claim outcomes</li>\n<li>Evaluate hidden exposures tied to other structures, ADUs, home businesses, and short-term rentals</li>\n<li>Strengthen coverage with endorsements such as Ordinance or Law, sewer backup, extended replacement cost, and personal injury</li>\n<li>Position yourself as a trusted advisor in an era of DIY online policy purchases</li>\n</ul>\n</dd>\n</div>\n</dl>\n<div class=\"card__btn-container\">\n<span data-is-available=\"true\" data-item-id=\"82139\" data-price=\"79.00\" data-product=\"Beyond the Four Walls: Hidden Homeowners Exposures and the Power of Endorsements\" data-react-component-id=\"webinar-cta\">\n<button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--fw-mobile btn--disabled\">Register - &amp;dollar;79.00</button>\n</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<section>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<article class=\"container__grid media-block__container media-block__container--reversed\">\n<div class=\"media-block__img-container\">\n<img alt=\"A pink piggy bank swims cutely in a bath of gold coins. \" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2023-05/Pig_In_Gold.jpg?itok=bMmCvybb\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2023-05/Pig_In_Gold.jpg?itok=bMmCvybb 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned_2x/public/2023-05/Pig_In_Gold.jpg?itok=wzo3tkhj  2x\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__header\">\n<h2 class=\"u-margin-hug\">\n            Enjoy unlimited access to webinars with CEU Unlimited.\n          </h2>\n<hr aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"hr hr--offset hr--md hr--md--offset hr--light\" role=\"presentation\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__content\">\n<p>As a new or current CEU Unlimited Subscriber, enjoy 12 months of full access to every CEU Webinar. That is in addition to 12 months unlimited access to our robust library of on-demand courses.</p><p>PLUS, there are NO state reporting and NO hidden fees for our webinars and on-demand courses– <strong>the price you see is the price you pay, period.</strong></p><p>Get your CEU Unlimited today.</p><p><em>*CEU Unlimited subscriber webinar discount will be reflected in the checkout process.</em><br/><em><span style=\"color:#A31E2C;\"><strong>No discount code or pre-paid agreement number required!</strong></span></em></p>\n<div class=\"card__btn-container card__btn-container--single\" data-item-id=\"31943\" data-learn-more-external=\"\" data-learn-more-text=\"\" data-learn-more-url=\"\" data-price=\"85.00\" data-product=\"CEU Unlimited Access Program\" data-react-component-id=\"add-to-cart\">\n<button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--disabled\">Add to Cart - &amp;dollar;</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width u-padding-bottom webinar-view-all\">\n<a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/webinars\" title=\"Webinars\">Back to all webinars</a>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div></body></html>",
